queries.query:
select ret_company_name as "Retail Company Name",
    dispatched_stn as "Store Dispatched LMP Station",
	inbound_stn as "Store Inbound LMP Station",
    ch_company_name as "Cash Handler Company Name",
    updated_date as "Updated Date",
    bank_reference_number as "Bank Reference Number",
    cashbag_number as "Cash Bag Number",
    schedule_no as "Schedule Number",
    schedule_date as "Schedule Date",
    store_number as "Store Number",
    grand_total_EUR as "Grand Total EUR",
    eur_paper as "EUR Paper",
    eur_coin as "EUR Coin",
    gbp_paper as "GBP Paper",
    gbp_coin as "GBP Coin",
    eur_from_gbp as "EUR from GBP",
	chf_paper as "CHF Paper",
    chf_coin as "CHF Coin",
    eur_from_chf as "EUR from CHF",
    EUR_from_other_accepted_currencies as "EUR from other Accepted Currencies"
   from report.rep_ch_till_balance_eu_paper_coin(
    $P{companyId},
    $P{effDate},
    $P{endDate},
    $P{bankRefNo},
    $P{depStationId},
    $P{arrStationId},
    $P{chCompanyId})
   order by schedule_date nulls first,
    store_number,
    cashbag_number
